==Useful Info==
'''Hellfire mortar''' is a construct that can fire [[Bolt of Magma|Bolts of Magma]] at enemies while swimming through [[lava]]. If its movement is blocked by an enemy, the mortal will sink back into lava.

{{monster spells|hellfire mortar}}

